REM Test HOLD and RELEASE with mouse buttons
REM This script tests holding mouse buttons down and releasing them
REM Note: Requires ENABLE_MOUSE flag during compilation

DELAY 1000

REM Hold left mouse button, move, then release (drag operation)
HOLD LEFTCLICK
DELAY 100
MOUSEMOVE 50 50
DELAY 100
MOUSEMOVE 50 0
DELAY 100
RELEASE LEFTCLICK
DELAY 1000

REM Test holding multiple buttons
HOLD LEFTCLICK
DELAY 200
HOLD RIGHTCLICK
DELAY 200
RELEASE LEFTCLICK
DELAY 200
RELEASE RIGHTCLICK
